#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md:1
msgid "Quickstart"
msgstr "クイックスタート"

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md:3
msgid "Install, open a save, and get analysis-ready data in under 5 minutes."
msgstr "インストールからセーブを開いて分析可能状態までを 5 分以内で．"

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md:5
msgid "Install"
msgstr "インストール"

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md:7
msgid "Install with the extras you need:"
msgstr "必要な extra を選んでインストール："

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md:17
msgid "Locate your save"
msgstr "セーブファイルの場所"

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md
msgid "Game"
msgstr "ゲーム"

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md
msgid "Default save folder (Windows)"
msgstr "デフォルトのセーブフォルダ (Windows)"

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md
msgid "Anno 1800"
msgstr "Anno 1800"

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md
msgid "``%USERPROFILE%\\Documents\\Anno 1800\\accounts\\<id>\\savegame\\``"
msgstr "``%USERPROFILE%\\Documents\\Anno 1800\\accounts\\<id>\\savegame\\``"

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md
msgid "Anno 117"
msgstr "Anno 117"

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md
msgid ""
"``%USERPROFILE%\\Documents\\Anno 117 - Pax "
"Romana\\accounts\\<id>\\savegame\\``"
msgstr ""
"``%USERPROFILE%\\Documents\\Anno 117 - Pax "
"Romana\\accounts\\<id>\\savegame\\``"

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md:24
msgid ""
"Copy a ``.a7s`` (Anno 1800) or ``.a8s`` (Anno 117) file somewhere "
"convenient. The tool is **read-only** — it never modifies your save."
msgstr ""
"``.a7s`` (Anno 1800) または ``.a8s`` (Anno 117) をどこか作業ディレクトリにコピーしてください．本ツールは"
" **読み取り専用** ─ セーブを書き換えません．"

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md:27
msgid "Auto-pick the latest save via `.env` (optional)"
msgstr "`.env` で最新 save を自動選択 (任意)"

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md:29
msgid ""
"If you do not want to type the save path every time, drop a ``.env`` in "
"the repo root pointing at your save directories. The CLI / GUI will pick "
"the **most recently modified** ``.a7s`` / ``.a8s`` under the directory "
"matching ``--title``."
msgstr ""
"毎回 save のパスを打つのが面倒なら，repo root に ``.env`` を置いて save "
"ディレクトリを指定してください．CLI / GUI は ``--title`` に対応するディレクトリ"
"配下から **最新 mtime** の ``.a7s`` / ``.a8s`` を自動で選びます．"

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md:40
msgid "With that in place, the save argument becomes optional:"
msgstr "これを設定しておけば，save 引数は省略可能になります："

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md:50
msgid "An explicit save path always wins over the ``.env`` lookup."
msgstr "save パスを明示的に渡した場合は，常に ``.env`` より優先されます．"

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md:52
msgid "Launch the TUI"
msgstr "TUI を起動"

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md:58
msgid ""
"Use ``Ctrl+T`` to switch screens (Overview → Trade Statistics → Supply "
"Balance). ``Ctrl+L`` toggles English/Japanese."
msgstr ""
"``Ctrl+T`` で画面切替 (Overview → Trade Statistics → Supply "
"Balance)．``Ctrl+L`` で英日切替．"

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md:61
msgid "Export the full state as JSON"
msgstr "全 state を JSON エクスポート"

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md:68
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The JSON contains overview + islands + tier breakdown + balance + every "
"TradeEvent. Load it with `pandas.read_json` / `pandas.json_normalize` and"
" you are analysis-ready (see {doc}`scm-analytics`)."
msgstr ""
"出力 JSON には概要・島情報・tier 別内訳・需給バランス・全 TradeEvent が含まれます．`pandas.read_json` /"
" `pandas.json_normalize` で読み込めば即分析可能です ({doc}`scm-analytics` を参照)．"

#: ../../source/guide/quickstart.md:72
msgid "One-liner Python API"
msgstr "Python API (ワンライナー)"

